[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "なかなか戻らないね……やっぱり探しに行こうかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00710",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そうでありますな。\n何か事故に巻き込まれているかもしれませぬ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00711",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なに言ってんのよ。そんなわけないじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00712",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ヨハナ！　大丈夫？　心配してたんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00713",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "悪かったわよ……突然飛び出していったりして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00714",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "その……ごめんね。あの後鬼門とも話したんだ。\nヨハナが嫌なら、無理強いしちゃダメだって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00715",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "だから、ヨハナはヨハナのやりたいように\nやるでござるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00716",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はあ？　当たり前じゃない。\n私は私のやりたいようにやるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00717",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "アイドル・ヨハナは、クールでありながら歌とダンスを\n完璧にこなす天才よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00718",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……そして、たまに素が出ちゃって、\nそれを恥ずかしがる……そんな子なの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00719",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "何か、吹っ切れた様子ですな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00720",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……思い出しただけよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00721",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "アイドルが立つステージは、アイドルの理想とファンの\n理想、両方があって成り立つものだということを",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00722",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "だから、私の理想を押し付けるだけじゃなくて、\nちゃんとファンの理想にも応えないと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00723",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "誰よりも私を推してくれてる、ファンのためにもね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00724",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00725",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……何よ！　なんか文句ある！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00726",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "あるわけがないでございましょう。\n拙者だって、同じ思いでありまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00727",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "アタシもアタシも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00728",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ふん……それならいいのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00729",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それにね、ヨハナ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00730",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "何よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00731",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "アタシは、どっちのヨハナも大好きだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00732",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "～～っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00733",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "うるさいわね！　あんたはそんなこと言ってる暇が\nあったらもっとダンスの練習しなさい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00734",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "完璧になるまでみっちり付きっ切りで\n教えてあげるわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00735",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "う……の、望むところだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00736",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00737",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まあ、一件落着、でありまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00738",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]